AeroSim API
===========

Provides RPCs to interact with the KSPAeroSim mod: capturing detached
aerodynamic models of a vessel, evaluating the aerodynamic force and torque
they experience at hypothetical flight states, analyzing pitch trim, and
running 6-DOF reentry predictions.

